		<div class="comment-content" style="display:block;">

			<p>Reading this article, âWhat Are Your Favorite Restaurants?â by Shannon Doyne, he states that the most appearance about restaurant where we eat every day at any time. The value, quickness, flavor and healthy food that they serve for the customer, are the most important things to take the right decision where they will go. I didnât eat McDonaldâs in my whole life, because I donât like any meat and fat food. Even though sometime I like to order pizza with less cheese, but most I like to order Mr. Wonton Chinese Restaurant. I love their Shrimp Fried Rice. McDonaldâs is a popular name in fast-food worlds. Itâs popular because of their cheap prize and also their less time to waste making foods. I think if they add some interesting and new item in their list with less fat, which will be more popular. We know that, people donât like the same menu that they eat every day. We always want something new to add our menu list. In the last paragraphs, they said that, people can make their own menu, but I think that can take more time and make trouble. People also have to be concern that, if you want something delicious, you have to wait minimum fifteen minute. Fast-food or restaurant peoples are not magic man  who will take two minute and give you delicious food!</p>

