			<p>Every day people are more conscious about what they eat. I think at this point people are not just looking for something cheap, fast, and delicious. They also are looking for something health with less fat and delicious too. I used to go to McDonald many years ago before I became in vegetarian, but now I know much more about food and how fast food was not good for me. Today I see fast food restaurant different than before, now there are many fast food restaurant which are not necessary unhealthy such as other. For example I work in a fast food restaurant of Lebanese food, where this concept is following the healthy way. I always see McDonald as a restaurant which is not healthy and have all limited menu.<br />
    Restaurant as Chipotle as other fast food restaurant has brought a concept of healthy and organic food. This has made people to open their mind and see other possibility to eat delicious food and healthier than others. Even though McDonald is still having a lot customer at this time, but I thinks is good that they try to introduce new a new concept of food, to make competition with the other companies that are growing up very fast even when they are more expensive. If I could create a fast food restaurant my concept would be a vegetarian fast restaurant. This restaurant will have all the imitations of meat, in that way people who are not vegetarian would like to try this kind of food. The concept of decoration it going to be young, with bright colors, and many picture hanging at the walls. This picture is going to educated people about what vegetarianism is; how my restaurant makes the food, the importance of protect animals, and the importance of healthy food. </p>
<p>   My restaurant is going to server three option, bowl, salads, roll, and burger.<br />
This option are  going to have vegetables, bread, all the imitation of meat.</p>

